title: Pablo Picasso 2024 Wall Calendar
description:
One of the most well known artists of the 20th century, and a leader in the modern art movement, Pablo Picasso was also the co-founder of cubism. Many of his most celebrated paintings are found in this gorgeous month to month wall calendar.

  • Dimensions: 12 x 12 in.
  • Includes major international holidays, lunar phases, and zodiac signs
  • Features 7 languages: Italian, English, German, French, Spanish, Portuguese, Japanese
